  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "Slice pumpkin into rounds and sweet red peppers.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over both vegetables, sprinkle with cumin powder, smoked paprika, oregano leaves, salt, mix well.",
    "Place the vegetables on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper. Roast for 25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "In an ice bath, shock roasted pumpkin and sweet red peppers to cool them quickly before serving.",
    "Serve warm with your choice of side dish."
